msgid "Need any supplies?  I got some skeleton repair beds upstairs too if you need 'em."
msgstr "需要什麼用品？如果你需要的話，我在樓上也有一些骷髏修理床。"

#. Id: 64663-rebirth.mod
#. -- Index: 1.0
#. -- Parent line: 0 (64659-rebirth.mod)
#. -- Speaker: Target (1)
#. -- Group title: shopkeep robo repair
#: 64663-rebirth.mod:0
msgid "What's a \"skeleton repair bed\"?"
msgstr "什麼是“骨架修理床”？"

#. Id: 64664-rebirth.mod
#. -- Index: 2.0
#. -- Parent line: 1 (64663-rebirth.mod)
#. -- Speaker: Me (0)
#. -- Group title: shopkeep robo repair
#: 64664-rebirth.mod:0
msgid "Y'know, when skeletons get worn out from too much fighting and patchwork repairs it starts to take it's toll.  A proper repair bed fixes 'em up good as new."
msgstr "你知道，當骷髏因過多的戰鬥和拼湊修理而疲憊不堪時，它就會開始造成傷害。一個合適的修理床可以很好地修復它們。"

#. Id: 95788-rebirth.mod
#. -- Index: 3.0
#. -- Parent line: 2 (64664-rebirth.mod)
#. -- Speaker: Me (0)
#. -- Group title: shopkeep robo repair
#: 95788-rebirth.mod:0
msgid "And sometimes hunters get their arms and legs eaten off, so they come use the beds to fit skeleton limbs on their stumps."
msgstr "有時候獵人會把他們的胳膊和腿吃掉，所以他們會用床來固定他們的樹樁上的骨架。"

